* Ensure switching between INX auto-attach and CNX manual attach is consistent
COLOR DEFAULT
* Start with default (likely INX auto-attach)
USE students
STATUS
STRUCT
LIST 5
* Move to CNX explicitly
USE students noindex
SETCNX students.cnx
STATUS
STRUCT INDEX
* Choose a CNX tag, verify reports
SETORDER students.cnx TAG LNAME --asc
STATUS
STRUCT INDEX
LIST 5
* Switch CNX tag & direction
SETORDER students.cnx TAG SID --desc
STATUS
STRUCT INDEX
LIST 5
* end
